ABOUT dwmblocks

    This directory contains dwmblocks source code.
    dwmblocks is a tiny utility for generating a status bar for dwm or
    similar programs.  There is an ability to generate status bar to
    stdout, that may be useful for dvtm(1) and similar programs.

    This dwmblocks distribution is a fork of torrinfail's dwmblocks as
    of commit a933ce0 (Thu Jan 6 2022) with the following differences:

        * fixed compilation of DragonFlyBSD
        * added man page
        * source code have been adjusted to suckless style

    See git log for complete differences.

    The original sources can be downloaded from:
    1. https://github.com/torrinfail/dwmblocks
    2. https://github.com/torrinfail/dwmblocks/archive/a933ce0/dwmblocks-a933ce0.zip

REQUIREMENTS

    * c99 compiler
    * POSIX sh(1p), make(1p) and "mandatory utilities"
    * pod2man(1pm) to prepare man page
    * libX11 is optional (disabled by "-DNO_X" flag)

INSTALL

    The shell command "make install" should build and install this
    package.  See ./config.mk file for configuration parameters.

    dwmblocks can be customized by creating a custom ./config.h and
    (re)compiling the source code.

